Module org.example.camping2
Package org.example.camping2.dto

Class Reserva

java.lang.Object
org.example.camping2.dto.Reserva
@Entity public class Reserva extends Object
Entity representing a reservation in the camping system. This class holds information about a reservation, including details about the client, resource, dates, total price, number of people, and accompanying guests. The entity is mapped to the `reserva` table in the database.
Since:
31/01/2025
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Andrews Dos Ramos
